ata-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3612741\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104edp1665702631104.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/edp1665702631104.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/edp1665702631104.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"edp1665702631104\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Draw 3-D Frame Outside (DrawOutside)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property determines whether a 3-D frame is drawn outside the widget area. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"edp1665702631104__section_pcw_nvh_wwb\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">DrawOutside=True</code>|<code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n      (default)</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"edp1665702631104__section_p4h_svh_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d351916e59\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"edp1665702631104__p_d103214e1_d103215e1_d103216e1\">Setting <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Draw 3-D Frame Outside</span>\n        to <code class=\"ph codeph\">false</code> prevents the widget from overlapping adjacent fields. For example,\n        on Windows 11, with the form's Cell Height set to 110, setting Draw Outside to true can\n        obscure the border of the field that has focus:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"edp1665702631104__table_d12164e1_d12165e1_d12166e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"edp1665702631104__table_d12164e1_d12165e1_d12166e1__entry__1\"> DrawOutside=False </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"edp1665702631104__table_d12164e1_d12165e1_d12166e1__entry__2\"> DrawOutside=True </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"edp1665702631104__table_d12164e1_d12165e1_d12166e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"edp1665702631104__fig_x3r_5vh_wwb\">\n<img alt=\"Image\" class=\"image\" id=\"edp1665702631104__image_igs_xvh_wwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/drawoutsidefalse_cellheight110.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"edp1665702631104__table_d12164e1_d12165e1_d12166e1__entry__2\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"edp1665702631104__fig_cjr_5vh_wwb\">\n<img alt=\"Image\" class=\"image\" id=\"edp1665702631104__image_hxh_zvh_wwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/drawoutsidetrue_cellheight110.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"edp1665702631104__p_d103217e1_d103218e1_d103219e1\">It is a static property and cannot be changed in\n        ProcScript.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"edp1665702631104__section_wvk_vvh_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d351916e129\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"edp1665702631104__table_d12167e1_d12168e1_d12169e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dynamic? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> No </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dependencies: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Applicable only if <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">3-D</span> is\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">true</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"edp1665702631104__section_omp_r23_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d351916e172\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"edp1665702631104__ul_hyd_s23_wwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"edp1665702631104__li_d41579e1_d41580e1_d41581e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sgr1665702639069.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sgr1665702639069.html\" title=\"The ueditbox widget is a field-level input control that enables the user to view and enter data in a field. It is applicable only to form components.\">ueditbox (EditBox)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"edp1665702631104__li_d41582e1_d41583e1_d41584e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vmo1688449724415.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vmo1688449724415.html\" title=\"The ucombobox widget combines an input field with a drop-down list. It allows users to select one item from a previously defined list, or enter their own data instead. It is applicable only to form components. Uniface provides a logical widget called ComboBox, which is mapped to ucombobox.\">ucombobox (Combo Box)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"edp1665702631104__li_d41585e1_d41586e1_d41587e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fud1688450548955.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fud1688450548955.html\" title=\"The udropdownlist widget is a field-level widget that can display a list of valid options in a list below the input field, so that the user can select one. It is applicable only to form components.\">udropdownlist (DropDownList)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"edp1665702631104__li_d41588e1_d41589e1_d41590e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ddd1665702643397.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ddd1665702643397.html\" title=\"The uoutputbox widget displays streaming text data. The data may come from a specified Output Channel, or be explicitly added. By default, it does not listen to any channel. Uniface provides a logical widget called OutputBox, which is mapped to uoutputbox.\">uoutputbox (OutputBox)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"edp1665702631104__li_d41591e1_d41592e1_d41593e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qwk1688451210612.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qwk1688451210612.html\" title=\"The urtfeditbox widget is used to display and edit text as Rich Text Format (RTF), which supports formatting such as font and color attributes, text alignment, indentation, and lists. Uniface provides a logical widget called RichEditBox, which is mapped to urtfeditbox.\">urtfeditbox (RichEditBox)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"edp1665702631104__li_d41594e1_d41595e1_d41596e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lxs1665702651483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lxs1665702651483.html\" title=\"The uspinbutton widget enables the user to enter or select a numeric value by clicking a button to increase or decrease a value by a predefined interval within a predefined range. Uniface provides a logical widget called SpinButton, which is mapped to uspinbutton.\">uspinbutton (SpinButton)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/txj1665702628158.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>3-D Effect (3d)</a><p>This property determines whether a three-dimensional appearance is applied when the widget is displayed. True (default) or False.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612741\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612741\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Draw 3-D Frame Outside (DrawOutside) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Draw 3-D Frame Outside (DrawOutside) This property determines whether a 3-D frame is drawn outside the widget area. DrawOutside=True | False (default) Description Setting Draw 3-D Frame Outside to false prevents the widget from overlapping adjacent fields. For example, on Windows 11, with the form's Cell Height set to 110, setting Draw Outside to true can obscure the border of the field that has focus: DrawOutside=False DrawOutside=True It is a static property and cannot be changed in ProcScript. Usage Dynamic? No Dependencies: Applicable only if 3-D is true . Applies To ueditbox (EditBox) ucombobox (Combo Box) udropdownlist (DropDownList) uoutputbox (OutputBox) urtfeditbox (RichEditBox) uspinbutton (SpinButton) Related Links 3-D Effect (3d) This property determines whether a three-dimensional appearance is applied when the widget is displayed. True (default) or False. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}